You must remember this: it's to make my name great.

00:56:52.708 --> 00:56:56.953
He said, and I said, 'Yes, Lord.

00:57:03.289 --> 00:57:03.538
I get it.

00:57:21.200 --> 00:57:21.531
But we will see signs and wonders like you wouldn't believe.

00:57:21.531 --> 00:57:24.880
' And the Lord said, 'I want you.

00:57:24.880 --> 00:57:29.920
' He's bringing these people into position right now.

00:57:29.920 --> 00:57:37.743
He's bringing in the last, the closers, the ones that are built for pressure.

00:57:37.743 --> 00:57:46.434
But to the ones that have a platform right now, 1 Corinthians 5:5, you'll see.

00:57:46.434 --> 00:57:51.611
Because they didn't do what he wanted them to do, it became about them.

00:57:54.619 --> 00:57:57.096
It wasn't about making his name great; it was about making theirs.

00:57:59.040 --> 00:58:06.133
And it became so much more that they get distracted.

00:58:06.133 --> 00:58:10.869
And that's why he said, 'I don't mind you having the money.

00:58:10.869 --> 00:58:14.320
I don't mind you having a nice jet.

00:58:14.320 --> 00:58:17.828
I don't mind you having a nice house.

00:58:17.828 --> 00:58:26.319
Those things are fine as long as they don't have you, as long as it is not a distraction.

00:58:55.460 --> 00:58:55.870
It's a tool; it's a tool for ministry.

00:58:55.870 --> 00:59:27.413
' And God doesn't want any of his people looking busted.

00:59:36.418 --> 00:59:37.546
You represent him.

00:59:37.546 --> 01:00:04.500
If you walk in a place and you look homely and you don't look like you've taken a bath in a week, and they look at you and go, 'You represent—?

01:00:04.500 --> 01:00:13.280
' He told me that's why, regarding my weight.

01:00:13.280 --> 01:00:24.594
I'm just being real; I'm just real transparent, y'all.

01:00:36.642 --> 01:01:16.022
I have nothing to hide from y'all, because if this thing goes away tomorrow and they come and say it's over, I'm going back to what I've always done.

01:01:16.022 --> 01:01:19.780
You'll catch me at a church somewhere sometime.

01:01:19.780 --> 01:01:33.069
But this is not me; I did this strictly because he asked me to.

01:01:33.069 --> 01:01:51.005
I'm telling you, it's a lot of pressure making sure you say the right things because you're in front of so many people now watching you.

01:01:51.005 --> 01:02:01.775
And me, Brandon, I just like my personal life and my privacy.

01:02:01.775 --> 01:02:42.879
I don't go around a lot of family; I've just been that way for a long time.

01:02:42.879 --> 01:03:07.240
I'm just me, and this whole thing has been a real trip for us—people seeing you in the grocery store and all that.

01:03:07.240 --> 01:04:12.014
I just go, 'Hey, I don't mind shaking your hand and being nice to you, but there are a lot of times I just like to get my food and go home.

01:04:12.014 --> 01:04:32.440
' And it's interesting; this whole thing's really interesting.

01:04:33.280 --> 01:04:41.349
And I'm not complaining, I'm just being real.

01:04:48.120 --> 01:04:48.489
And that's why he said about my weight.

01:04:48.489 --> 01:04:57.550
I've had all these dreams and he talks to me about representing him.

01:04:57.550 --> 01:05:01.480
God cares about how you look.

01:05:01.480 --> 01:05:06.319
God cares about how clean you look when you represent him.

01:05:06.319 --> 01:05:10.409
When you represent him, you dress for the job.

01:05:13.707 --> 01:05:14.480
You dress for the occasion.

01:05:14.480 --> 01:05:21.640
Well, if that's all you have and that's the best you look, he'll provide for more.

01:05:21.640 --> 01:05:23.039
I'm telling you.

01:05:23.039 --> 01:06:14.512
But I'm telling you, he even cares about how much weight you have on you and how you're taking care of your body.

01:06:14.512 --> 01:06:21.780
How many times he brings up gluttony in the Bible?

01:06:21.790 --> 01:07:38.684
How many times he brings up lust and all these other things in the Bible?

01:07:38.684 --> 01:07:40.960
There are things that are his pet peeves, I'm telling you.

01:07:40.960 --> 01:08:24.701
And taking care of yourself—he talks about being a glutton all the time.

01:08:24.701 --> 01:09:04.390
And I start looking; he starts showing it to me in these dreams and I go, 'Well, I'll be.

01:09:04.400 --> 01:09:11.805
My people perish for a lack of knowledge.

01:09:11.805 --> 01:09:29.440
' And I start going, 'Well, if it means that much to you, you know, I want to represent you well.

01:09:35.486 --> 01:09:36.011
I want to talk well.

01:09:36.011 --> 01:10:06.693
When my words come out of my mouth, I don't want to sound like some backwoods person who doesn't have a lot of education.

01:10:06.693 --> 01:11:25.669
' And I don't, but I say what he tells me to say and I do it the best I can and I keep my heart right.

01:11:50.400 --> 01:11:50.663
You know, she has an education.

01:11:50.663 --> 01:11:57.030
She has a master's degree.

01:11:57.040 --> 01:12:15.893
Brandon, he barely has a GED.

01:12:15.893 --> 01:12:49.595
But thank God for a pretty wife this smart.

01:12:49.595 --> 01:12:52.719
I'm blessed.

01:13:07.940 --> 01:13:08.280
But I go, 'Thank God.

01:13:08.280 --> 01:13:15.135
' And thank God for a son that's very smart.

01:13:15.135 --> 01:13:22.020
Between Braden and Diana, they've got the brains over here.

01:13:32.907 --> 01:13:33.253
I go, 'Hey you guys, I appreciate you cutting me slack.

01:13:33.253 --> 01:13:36.029
' But all glory to Jesus.

01:13:36.029 --> 01:13:37.430
Let's take communion.

01:13:37.430 --> 01:13:40.329
I've rambled here long enough.

01:13:40.329 --> 01:13:51.600
Braden says it's been an hour; it keeps me up to date.

01:14:06.800 --> 01:14:07.040
And the other guy said, 'What are you doing tapping like that?

01:14:07.040 --> 01:14:09.440
' That's me saying that's time.

01:14:09.440 --> 01:14:12.888
That's me trying to see how long I've been rambling.

01:14:12.888 --> 01:14:15.547
How many people are watching?

01:14:36.800 --> 01:14:37.072
I want to know, did I scare them all away?

01:14:37.072 --> 01:14:39.520
If they're not here, I'm going home.

01:15:02.680 --> 01:15:02.870
I'm going to go in there and sit in front of my TV and watch Kathryn Kuhlman or something.

01:15:02.870 --> 01:15:05.240
If they aren't interested, neither am I.

01:15:05.240 --> 01:15:31.520
I'll go watch Billy Burke for a little bit and feed myself.

01:16:43.344 --> 01:16:43.808
Father, I thank you, Lord, for all that you've done for me.

01:17:03.579 --> 01:17:03.869
You've been so good to us, Father, and I'm so thankful for your friendship.

01:17:03.869 --> 01:17:12.260
I'm so thankful for all that you've provided.

01:17:12.260 --> 01:17:19.440
I'm thankful, Father, for these people that are here—6,400 or whatever.

01:17:19.440 --> 01:17:24.970
I'm thankful, Father, for every single one of these people.

01:17:24.970 --> 01:17:27.396
And they all have needs.

01:17:27.396 --> 01:17:42.110
They don't want to waste their time on here; they all want a touch from Jesus.

01:17:42.110 --> 01:17:47.253
And I know that, Father, you're no respecter of persons.

01:18:08.480 --> 01:18:17.750
And I'm asking you, Father, to become real to every single one of them.

01:18:17.760 --> 01:18:27.900
I'm asking you, just as much as you've become real to me, that you said, 'Those that seek me will find me.

01:18:27.900 --> 01:18:32.969
Those that knock, the door will be opened unto them.

01:18:32.969 --> 01:18:50.392
' And the things you show me—the secret things, the hidden things that I can't even talk about on here.

01:18:50.392 --> 01:18:56.719
Father, I thank you that you visit me.

01:18:56.719 --> 01:18:58.159
I thank you, God.

01:18:58.159 --> 01:19:16.544
You could visit anybody, but Father, the eyes of the Lord run to and fro throughout the whole earth looking for a heart who's perfect towards you.

01:19:16.544 --> 01:19:20.112
And Lord, I don't always have the right heart, I'm sure.

01:19:30.480 --> 01:19:37.940
But Father, I thank you, Lord, that our hearts get better and better every single day.

01:19:37.940 --> 01:19:44.740
That you create in us a clean heart, Father.

01:20:21.719 --> 01:20:22.212
That we're better in our marriage, we're better with our children, we're better as husbands and fathers as we lead our family.

01:20:26.480 --> 01:20:28.116
And Father, I thank you, Lord, for the people that are on here tonight.

01:20:28.116 --> 01:20:29.858
They're hungry.

01:20:29.858 --> 01:20:37.699
It's so late at night and they're all on here.

01:20:37.699 --> 01:20:44.080
Father, there are people that are just wanting to know what's coming.

01:20:44.080 --> 01:20:53.644
Some of them are freaked out, but some of them are desperate because they just want a touch from Jesus and they want something authentic.

01:20:53.644 --> 01:20:57.966
They're tired of Christian fakeness; they're looking for authenticity.

01:21:03.049 --> 01:21:05.558
And Father, I thank you, Lord, that every single one of them, Father, find what they're looking for.

01:21:31.920 --> 01:21:32.200
That you touch them like you've touched me.

01:21:32.200 --> 01:21:37.720
That you touch them, Father, and they lack no good thing.

01:21:37.720 --> 01:21:45.120
That their hearts are full of faith and their eyes are full of hope.

01:21:45.120 --> 01:21:52.550
Their minds, Father, are looking towards you because you're the author and the finisher.

01:22:10.986 --> 01:22:11.280
That, Father, you're the friend, you're the helper, you're everything.

01:22:16.902 --> 01:22:19.839
And Father, I thank you, Lord, that you become real to them.

01:22:19.839 --> 01:22:22.560
You become real to them.

01:22:40.267 --> 01:22:40.693
And Father, I thank you, Lord, that the bondage of doubt and unbelief is broken off of their life.

01:23:14.880 --> 01:23:15.190
Father, I thank you, Lord, that they'll become so desperate—so desperate that you'll be just like air.

01:23:15.190 --> 01:23:19.728
How bad do you want that next breath?

01:23:19.728 --> 01:23:35.355
How bad do you want that drink of water when you're outside in the heat?

01:23:35.355 --> 01:23:59.440
How bad do you want food when you haven't had it in a long time, Father?

01:23:59.440 --> 01:24:32.339
That when we're so in pursuit of you that we lose ourselves in it, that we lose ourselves in trying to find you.

01:24:32.339 --> 01:24:34.560
Father, you said those that seek you will find you.

01:24:34.560 --> 01:24:49.020
And I thank you, Father, that today is a day of a turnaround in many of their lives.

01:24:49.020 --> 01:24:56.314
That this isn't just another wafer and another thing of juice; it represents something.

01:24:56.314 --> 01:25:00.280
That Jesus Christ is a healer.

01:25:00.280 --> 01:25:13.996
That Jesus Christ paid the price for every single one of us to walk in victory.

01:25:13.996 --> 01:25:33.160
That the blood of Jesus reigns supreme over every demonic principality, power, spiritual wickedness in high places, witchcraft, voodoo, whatever it may be.

01:25:43.280 --> 01:25:43.840
Jesus paid the price and he's defeated every single one of them.

01:25:43.840 --> 01:25:47.706
Jesus did it.

01:25:47.706 --> 01:25:52.239
And it's by his blood we are free.

01:25:52.239 --> 01:25:54.400
Jesus paid the price for me.

01:25:54.400 --> 01:26:12.590
No matter how many people try to curse me, no matter how many people try to hex me, Jesus paid the price for me to walk in victory.

01:26:35.874 --> 01:26:36.229
And he gave me authority over the devil.

01:26:36.229 --> 01:26:53.840
Father, I thank you, Lord, that no weapon formed against us is going to prosper.

01:26:53.840 --> 01:27:00.320
Every tongue that rises against us, we condemn it; it falls to the ground.

01:27:00.320 --> 01:27:07.520
It doesn't even bear fruit because you cannot curse whom God has blessed.

01:27:07.520 --> 01:27:12.840
Jesus Christ blessed me.

01:27:33.652 --> 01:27:33.906
A curse without a cause cannot stand and has no cause because of the blood of Jesus.

01:27:33.906 --> 01:27:39.634
I am washed in the blood of Jesus.

01:27:39.634 --> 01:28:12.960
He is the accuser of the brethren, but he can't accuse me because there's nothing to accuse; it's all under the blood.

01:28:12.960 --> 01:28:41.199
Everything you've done wrong today, as you take this, is under the blood.

01:29:08.000 --> 01:29:09.200
What can wash away my sin?

01:29:09.200 --> 01:29:17.231
Nothing but the blood of Jesus.

01:29:38.266 --> 01:29:38.533
What can make me whole again?

01:29:38.533 --> 01:29:40.469
Nothing but the blood of Jesus.

01:29:40.469 --> 01:29:44.230
I'm so thankful, Father, for that blood and for your healing.

01:29:50.849 --> 01:29:56.719
I thank you, Father, that we walk in divine health and we take this body in Jesus' name.

01:29:56.719 --> 01:30:07.440
We thank you, Father, that what you bore in your body, we need not bear in ours.

01:30:07.440 --> 01:30:20.010
According to Galatians 3:13, Christ has redeemed us from the curse of the law.

01:30:20.010 --> 01:30:29.200
We take this body right now in Jesus' name.

01:30:29.200 --> 01:30:30.160
Isn't Jesus wonderful?

01:30:30.160 --> 01:30:31.120
I just believe it.

01:30:31.120 --> 01:30:49.307
Father, we thank you for the authority of the believer and the power in the blood.

01:31:17.600 --> 01:31:19.840
We take the blood and we apply it to our lives, our president, our homes, and our finances, so that we lack no good thing.

01:31:19.840 --> 01:31:32.250
There's more than enough in the account, in your finances, and in your job.

01:31:32.250 --> 01:31:43.580
You're the top person at the job, anointed in a way that the world is not familiar with, all for the glory of God.

01:31:53.749 --> 01:31:54.114
We make much of the blood and apply it to our lives right now.

01:31:54.114 --> 01:32:02.800
We thank you, Lord, for all that you've done for us in Jesus' name.

01:32:02.800 --> 01:32:08.857
We confess our sins; it's all under the blood.

01:32:08.857 --> 01:32:16.587
I have my Rose of Sharon oil that Billy Burke got me for Christmas last year.

01:32:32.130 --> 01:32:32.480
I anoint my head; you should too.

01:32:35.909 --> 01:32:38.747
I won't put a lot on you because it will run down your face; I know better now.

01:32:48.239 --> 01:32:56.320
Father, I cover my mind and my spiritual eyes so that I have eyes to see what the Spirit shows me, uninterrupted and unhindered by any satanic or demonic force.

01:32:56.320 --> 01:33:01.863
We plead the blood right now in Jesus' name.

01:33:07.360 --> 01:33:10.420
Father, we thank you for showing us that which is to come, as we look through the veil.

01:33:23.320 --> 01:33:23.653
Now we take the water.

01:33:23.653 --> 01:33:36.440
I'll pray with you just a little bit longer, about 25 minutes.

01:33:36.440 --> 01:33:50.880
I'm trying to come on earlier for you folks, but we'll get better at it; there is a lot going on right now.

01:33:59.679 --> 01:34:01.096
Father, we thank you.

01:34:01.096 --> 01:34:09.580
Many of you—6,400 of you—I feel the anointing so strong on me, especially on my spiritual eyes.

01:34:09.580 --> 01:34:12.228
Now I see two different paths.

01:34:12.228 --> 01:34:17.500
I want you to pray with me for Erica, Charlie's widow.

01:34:37.540 --> 01:34:37.800
I want to lift this young woman up.

01:34:46.720 --> 01:34:47.040
I see a storm—a very serious one.

01:34:47.040 --> 01:35:06.876
She's already been through a major storm, but that was just the beginning of the eye of the hurricane.

01:35:06.876 --> 01:35:12.000
We pray a hedge of protection around her.

01:35:12.000 --> 01:35:19.022
Every false accuser and lying tongue that would come against her, I thank you that only truth will prevail.

01:35:19.022 --> 01:35:22.110
Every false witness and lying spirit is bound in Jesus' name.

01:35:22.110 --> 01:35:24.480
You're the lifter of the heart and the countenance.

01:35:24.480 --> 01:35:35.920
Sometimes we walk through the valley of the shadow of death, but we fear no evil; your rod and your staff comfort us.

01:35:35.920 --> 01:35:44.182
Do not cast down your confidence when the waves and storms of life come against you.

01:35:44.182 --> 01:35:59.880
Look to the hills from which our help comes; our help comes from the Lord who made heaven and earth.

01:35:59.880 --> 01:36:14.480
But he dwells on the inside of you now, so we look inward to the Holy Spirit and say, 'Father, you're the lifter of my head and my countenance.

01:36:14.480 --> 01:36:20.288
' We cast not down our confidence; we don't give up or be weary in well-doing.

01:36:20.288 --> 01:36:29.480
Verily, verily, all hidden things be revealed—an uncovering—for there is much more here than what you see.

01:36:29.480 --> 01:36:31.794
I see the rabbit hole.

01:36:31.794 --> 01:36:39.260
Conspiracies are not so much a conspiracy; it's not what it seems.

01:36:39.260 --> 01:36:44.133
I see the Alice in Wonderland rabbit standing at the rabbit hole.

01:36:44.133 --> 01:36:46.000
He's late.

01:36:46.000 --> 01:36:49.622
I see a black hat.

01:37:09.497 --> 01:37:09.771
Now I see Candace Owens' face.

01:37:17.999 --> 01:37:18.159
What does she see?

01:37:18.159 --> 01:37:21.331
She's standing in front of a computer, looking at an email.

01:37:21.331 --> 01:37:22.960
We pray for her protection.

01:37:22.960 --> 01:37:25.653
She's getting too close to something in the rabbit hole.

01:37:25.653 --> 01:37:35.440
Her eyes are wide, like Puss in Boots when his eyes get really big as he's looking at something.

01:37:42.899 --> 01:37:43.289
I see her looking at the computer, and even Alex Jones' face comes up.

01:37:43.289 --> 01:37:49.813
Alex Jones knows, but he won't touch it; he has other things to focus on.

01:38:04.848 --> 01:38:05.136
I see his face.

01:38:05.136 --> 01:38:06.933
He turned it.

01:38:06.933 --> 01:38:11.565
Alex Jones, and he could see the computer screen.

01:38:11.565 --> 01:38:19.200
He was looking at it, but he didn't have the eyes for it.

01:38:19.200 --> 01:38:26.036
I could see him turn, but he's more focused on the country and what is coming to the nation.

01:38:26.036 --> 01:38:29.417
She's on a mission for something else.

01:38:50.446 --> 01:38:50.709
I don't know why I'm going, "Lord, why did you call me to do this tonight?

01:38:51.234 --> 01:38:52.400
" but I do it.

01:38:52.400 --> 01:38:53.360
Heavy hearts.

01:38:53.680 --> 01:38:55.800
You will say heavy hearts.

01:38:55.800 --> 01:39:02.418
The Lord said heavy hearts, for the rabbit hole is not such a rabbit hole.

01:39:02.418 --> 01:39:06.544
We pray over her today.

01:39:06.544 --> 01:39:14.180
We thank you, Lord, that she'll have a radical visitation and she'll become a bigger mouthpiece for you.

01:39:14.180 --> 01:39:23.327
It won't be about fame and it won't be about fortune, but she'll have a radical visitation with you.

01:39:23.327 --> 01:39:32.280
She'll find the true call of what you've called her to do.

01:39:32.280 --> 01:39:40.320
Candace Owens, you'll find your true call for what God has called you to do on a greater level.

01:39:42.617 --> 01:39:49.466
The platform is just for the people to bring it, but God's going to use something more if you will just yield it to him.

01:40:06.746 --> 01:40:07.004
He said you will soar if you will just yield to him; there's more that he has for you behind another door.

01:40:07.004 --> 01:40:08.658
There is greater influence.

01:40:08.658 --> 01:40:14.276
You've hit a plateau for what he's wanting to do to take you to the next level.

01:40:14.276 --> 01:40:20.373
This door is a big door, and there are carvings all on the front of it.

01:40:37.792 --> 01:40:38.480
This has to do with him.

01:40:38.480 --> 01:40:51.200
What you've achieved so far has had a hand, but what he wants to take you to do is on another level concerning this young girl.

01:40:53.901 --> 01:40:54.699
I don't know much about her, but I've seen her.

01:40:54.699 --> 01:40:55.240
Great influence.

01:41:03.910 --> 01:41:04.280
The Lord wants to do even on a greater level.

01:41:05.390 --> 01:41:08.293
I delivered the word, and it's out of my thought.

01:41:08.293 --> 01:41:13.509
It flowed the way he said it; it was beautiful.

01:41:13.509 --> 01:41:22.772
He wants to do something so much more, to release it all for his glory.

01:41:22.772 --> 01:41:25.467
He's bringing you to a new door.

01:41:25.467 --> 01:41:26.120
Politics.

01:41:26.120 --> 01:41:32.746
Being like the Cortez girl, she's sold for the radical left.

01:41:32.746 --> 01:41:39.159
She'll be a radical right even at a greater capacity with her mouth.

01:41:58.959 --> 01:41:59.359
But there are things that have turned.

01:41:59.359 --> 01:42:06.711
God wants to take her from there to there, but she has to surrender to him.

01:42:06.711 --> 01:42:17.751
He said, "Surrender to me all that you have, and I'll take you to the next level.

01:42:17.751 --> 01:42:26.933
" He's had his hand on you, but he wants to take you to the next level.

01:42:31.497 --> 01:42:38.610
I see this next level as a greater level with you.

01:42:49.943 --> 01:42:52.159
You think the influence you've had so far is nothing compared to what God wants to do with you if you yield to him and call out to him.

01:42:52.159 --> 01:42:53.659
Yield your heart to him.

01:42:55.180 --> 01:42:55.800
Sell out to Jesus; lose the pride.

01:42:55.800 --> 01:43:01.360
He has great voices that he wants to use, like Alex Jones.

01:43:01.360 --> 01:43:02.180
Very interesting.

01:43:03.940 --> 01:43:05.980
I see Alex, but Tucker is so far out there.

01:43:05.980 --> 01:43:07.060
Alex is closer.

01:43:07.060 --> 01:43:10.530
You see levels of where they are with the Lord.

01:43:10.530 --> 01:43:15.097
Tucker's out there; Alex is just right there.

01:43:15.097 --> 01:43:17.719
Become like a John the Baptist.

